Assign pi 4*atan(1)

Image rxMat3 		3 3 1 float
Image ryMat3 		3 3 1 float
Image rzMat3 		3 3 1 float
Image rxMat4 		4 4 1 float
Image ryMat4 		4 4 1 float
Image rzMat4 		4 4 1 float
